en_results.text: Messrs. Hong Kong Electric Co. Ltd.,
With reference to your letter ref.D & P/84l/A/014l dated 9th
November 1987 and the recent discussions between your Mr. S.L.Lok and our
Mr. K.M. Au Yeung and Mr. M.H. Luk, I wish to confirm the following points :-
(a) Your new requirements on the cable trenches inside
transformers room will be provide. However, since
these new requirements have just been make known
to us, it was agreed that these provisions would
not affect the scheduled hand/take over of the
(b) For the ventilation system, since the Noise Control
Bill 1987 has not been enacted, we will provide the
system according to the existing standard.
Finally, please find enclosed two copies of our sketch no.
ITφ3-SK l showing your new requirements on cable trenches of
room for your confirmation and retention.
